%% Sensia POC — High-level workflow (input → response)
flowchart TB
  Start([User starts session])
  Input{How does user send input?}

  Start --> Input

  Input -->|Type text| T1[React UI: sendChat]
  Input -->|Record mic| T2[React UI: sendMicAudio]
  Input -->|Upload file| T3[React UI: analyzeAudioFile]

  T1 --> API1[POST /chat]
  T2 --> API2[POST /mic]
  T3 --> API3[POST /audio/analyze]

  API1 --> Ask
  API2 --> Whisper[Whisper: speech → text]
  API3 --> Whisper
  API3 --> Voice[librosa + Groq voice report]

  Whisper --> Ask[ask_question]
  Voice --> Ask

  Ask --> Guard{Input guardrails?}

  Guard -->|Block: off-topic / crisis / harmful| Refuse[Canned reply — no therapy LLM]
  Guard -->|Allow: in scope| Memory[Load Redis turns + session summary]
  Memory --> RAG[Chroma RAG: top 3 chunks]
  RAG --> Prompt[Build prompt + scope rules]
  Prompt --> LLM[Groq: generate therapy reply]

  Refuse --> Save[Save turn to Redis / memory]
  LLM --> Save

  Save --> JSON[API JSON response]
  JSON --> UI[React UI: show message in chat]
  UI --> Toast{guardrail_triggered?}
  Toast -->|Yes| Notify[Toast: crisis or blocked]
  Toast -->|No| Done
  Notify --> Done

  UI --> TTSopt{User clicks Play TTS?}
  TTSopt -->|Yes| TTS[POST /tts → Edge MP3]
  TTSopt -->|No| End([Done])
  TTS --> Hear[User hears audio]
  Hear --> End
  Done --> TTSopt

  style Start fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#6c8ebf
  style Input fill:#ffe6cc,stroke:#d79b00
  style Guard fill:#f8cecc,stroke:#b85450
  style Refuse fill:#f8cecc,stroke:#b85450
  style LLM fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#d6b656
  style JSON fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#6c8ebf
  style End fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
